import Vue from 'vue'
import App from './App.vue'
import router from './router'
import axios from 'axios'
import SlideVerify from 'vue-monoplasty-slide-verify'

Vue.use(SlideVerify)

Vue.config.productionTip = false
Vue.prototype.axios = axios

new Vue({
  axios,
  SlideVerify,
  router,
  render: h => h(App)
}).$mount('#app')
